# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Consensus Algorithms Basics

🔥 Very important distributed systems topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

In distributed systems:

👉 many machines must agree on one value/state.

This agreement process is called:

👉 Consensus

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Group deciding meeting time 📅

Everyone must agree on one final decision.

---

## Why Difficult?

Machines may:

❌ fail
❌ respond slowly
❌ lose network connection

---

## Popular Algorithms

* Raft
* Paxos

(You only need basics for placements.)

---

## Uses

✔ databases
✔ distributed systems
✔ leader election

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why consensus algorithms are needed?**

👉 To maintain consistency and agreement across distributed systems.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="k8m2vx"
Consensus = all nodes agree
```

